Creates a note for the passed refid using the title & contents.
    Can create alert notes if supplied with the appropriate keywords.

    @param refid: String reference id for the new note to be made.
    @param title: String title of the note.
    @param contents: String contents for the body of the note.
    @param alert_date: Datetime used for building an alert note that will
                       send an email containg the note at this date & time.
    @param alert_email: String email address used to send the alert note.
